\int 1 dt=\int\frac{1}{\sin z-1}dz \\=\int\frac{1}{\sin z-1}.\frac{\sin z+1}{\sin z+1}dz \\=\int\frac{\sin z+1}{-\cos^2 z}dz
z = y - t
