t+c=-\sec z-\tan z=-\frac{1+\sin z}{\cos z}
1+\sin z=1+\cos (\frac{\pi}{2}-z)=1+\cos v=1+2\cos^2 \frac{v}{2}-1=2\cos^2 \frac{v}{2} \\ \cos z=\sin(\frac{\pi}{2}-z)=\sin v=2\sin\frac{v}{2}\cos\frac{v}{2}
t+c=\cot\frac{v}{2}
